data.description: The LOWEST $/SQFT listing anywhere in Viewpoint at $221/SQFT! Priced below comps to allow you to make the updates and choose the fresh paint color you'd like in your new home. Here's your chance to put the finishing touches on a great home in a beautiful community. Located in a quiet gated community, this gem of a residence features a large primary suite with an oversized walk-in closet and a separate shower and garden tub, a light and bright kitchen, a wet bar, and a 3-car garage! Enjoy the fresh air and mountain views from your covered patio in the low-maintenance backyard, or from the beautiful courtyard out front. The cozy fireplace in the living room is perfect for the cooler weather. Don't miss the opportunity to make this charming Prescott Valley gated home your own!
